des: "For a quick snack, I buy the small tortilla shells in the refrigerated section in the store. I then spread peanut butter and or bananas/raisins on, fold and serve. In the morning, I have added a little honey on top."
ins: Lay tortilla flat.  Spread peanut butter and honey on tortilla.  Place banana in the middle and sprinkle in the raisins.  Wrap, and serve.
